import React, { Component } from "react"
import { ProfileWrap, Left, List, Link } from "./styles/profile"

class Profile extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <ProfileWrap>
          <Left>
            <List>
              <Link>Profile</Link>
              <Link>Bookings</Link>
              <Link>Payment</Link>
              <Link>Reviews</Link>
            </List>
          </Left>
        </ProfileWrap>
      </>
    )
  }
}
export default Profile
